Bucket is UNOFFICIAL app for Substratum Theme Engine

THIS APP REQUIRES NOUGAT ROM WITH OMS SUPPORT OR OREO (ROOTED OR WITH SUBSTRATUM SERVICE)

NOTE: This app is not affiliate with Substratum team. Please don't post bug reports to official Substratum groups/chats.

For now this app contains only overlay support.

